{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1071,"text":"I would like to share with you\na new model of higher education,"},{"time":5502,"text":"a model that, once expanded,"},{"time":8308,"text":"can enhance the collective intelligence"},{"time":10650,"text":"of millions of creative\nand motivated individuals"},{"time":15143,"text":"that otherwise would be left behind."},{"time":18250,"text":"Look at the world."},{"time":20001,"text":"Pick a place and focus on it."},{"time":22664,"text":"You will find humans\nchasing higher education."},{"time":27187,"text":"Let's meet some of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29354,"text":"Patrick."},{"time":30821,"text":"Patrick was born in Liberia\nto a family of 20 children."},{"time":36380,"text":"During the civil war,"},{"time":38004,"text":"he and his family were forced\nto flee to Nigeria."},{"time":42468,"text":"There, in spite of his situation,"},{"time":45230,"text":"he graduated high school\nwith nearly perfect grades."},{"time":49389,"text":"He wanted to continue to higher education,"},{"time":52477,"text":"but due to his family\nliving on the poverty line,"},{"time":55761,"text":"he was soon sent to South Africa"},{"time":58292,"text":"to work and send back money\nto feed his family."},{"time":63036,"text":"Patrick never gave up his dream\nof higher education."},{"time":66892,"text":"Late at night, after work,"},{"time":69315,"text":"he surfed the net,\nlooking for ways to study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73827,"text":"Meet Debbie."},{"time":75117,"text":"Debbie is from Florida."},{"time":77897,"text":"Her parents didn't go to college,\nand neither did any of her siblings."},{"time":82706,"text":"Debbie has worked all her life,"},{"time":86013,"text":"pays taxes, supports herself\nmonth to month,"},{"time":89847,"text":"proud of the American dream,"},{"time":92199,"text":"a dream that just won't be complete\nwithout higher education."},{"time":96870,"text":"But Debbie doesn't have the savings\nfor higher education."},{"time":100613,"text":"She can't pay the tuition."},{"time":102881,"text":"Neither could she leave work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106094,"text":"Meet Wael."},{"time":107750,"text":"Wael is from Syria."},{"time":109910,"text":"He's experiencing firsthand"},{"time":113528,"text":"the misery, fear and failure\nimposed on his country."},{"time":118755,"text":"He's a big believer in education."},{"time":121330,"text":"He knew that if he could find\nan opportunity for higher education,"},{"time":125387,"text":"an opportunity to get ahead of the rest,"},{"time":128206,"text":"he has a better chance to survive\nin a world turned upside down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134057,"text":"The higher education system"},{"time":137495,"text":"failed Patrick, Debbie and Wael,"},{"time":140241,"text":"exactly as it is failing\nmillions of potential students --"},{"time":145210,"text":"millions that graduate high school,"},{"time":148187,"text":"millions that are qualified\nfor higher education,"},{"time":151599,"text":"millions that want to study\nyet cannot access it for various reasons."},{"time":157618,"text":"First: financial."},{"time":160412,"text":"Universities are expensive;\nwe all know it."},{"time":163331,"text":"In large parts of the world,"},{"time":165459,"text":"higher education is unattainable\nfor an average citizen."},{"time":170258,"text":"This is probably the biggest problem\nfacing our society."},{"time":174672,"text":"Higher education stopped\nbeing a right for all"},{"time":178282,"text":"and became a privilege for the few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181971,"text":"Second: cultural."},{"time":186061,"text":"Students who are qualified\nfor higher education"},{"time":188914,"text":"can afford -- want to study -- cannot,"},{"time":192970,"text":"because it is not decent,\nit is not a place for a woman."},{"time":199047,"text":"This is the story of countless women\nin Africa, for example,"},{"time":203010,"text":"prevented from higher education\nbecause of cultural barriers."},{"time":207686,"text":"And here comes the third reason:"},{"time":210110,"text":"UNESCO stated that in 2025,"},{"time":213946,"text":"100 million students will be deprived\nof higher education,"},{"time":219614,"text":"simply because there will not be enough\nseats to accommodate them,"},{"time":224608,"text":"to meet the demand."},{"time":226363,"text":"They will take a placement test,\nthey will pass it,"},{"time":229556,"text":"but they still won't have access,\nbecause there are no places available."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235416,"text":"These are the reasons\nI founded University of the People,"},{"time":240140,"text":"a nonprofit, tuition-free,\ndegree-granting university"},{"time":245047,"text":"to give an alternative,"},{"time":246858,"text":"to create an alternative,\nto those who have no other;"},{"time":250376,"text":"an alternative that will be\naffordable and scalable,"},{"time":255841,"text":"an alternative that will disrupt\nthe current education system,"},{"time":261725,"text":"and open the gates to higher education\nfor every qualified student"},{"time":265917,"text":"regardless of what they earn,\nwhere they live,"},{"time":270553,"text":"or what society says about them."},{"time":273449,"text":"Patrick, Debbie and Wael"},{"time":275445,"text":"are only three examples\nout of the 1,700 accepted students"},{"time":279095,"text":"from 143 countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283492,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":284896,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286196,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":288028,"text":"We didn't need to reinvent the wheel."},{"time":290273,"text":"We just looked at what wasn't working"},{"time":292809,"text":"and used the amazing power of the Internet"},{"time":295572,"text":"to get around it."},{"time":297386,"text":"We set out to build a model"},{"time":300928,"text":"that will cut down almost entirely\nthe cost of higher education."},{"time":305927,"text":"And that's how we did it."},{"time":307869,"text":"First, bricks and mortar cost money."},{"time":311324,"text":"Universities have expenses\nthat virtual universities don't."},{"time":316470,"text":"We don't need to pass these expenses\non to our students."},{"time":320124,"text":"They don't exist."},{"time":321528,"text":"We also don't need\nto worry about capacity."},{"time":324671,"text":"There are no limits of seats\nin virtual university."},{"time":328867,"text":"Actually, nobody needs to stand\nat the back of the lecture hall."},{"time":333228,"text":"Textbooks are also something\nour students don't need to buy."},{"time":337803,"text":"By using open educational resources"},{"time":340731,"text":"and the generosity of professors"},{"time":343211,"text":"who are putting their material up\nfree and accessible,"},{"time":347747,"text":"we don't need to send\nour students to buy textbooks."},{"time":350523,"text":"All of our materials come free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353635,"text":"Even professors,"},{"time":355265,"text":"the most expensive line\nin any university balance sheet,"},{"time":359160,"text":"come free to our students."},{"time":360840,"text":"Over 3,000 of them,"},{"time":363611,"text":"including presidents, vice chancellors,\nprofessors and academic advisers"},{"time":369648,"text":"from top universities such as NYU,\nYale, Berkeley and Oxford,"},{"time":375224,"text":"came on board to help our students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378200,"text":"Finally, is our belief\nin peer-to-peer learning."},{"time":382394,"text":"We use this sound pedagogical model"},{"time":385624,"text":"to encourage our students\nfrom all over the world"},{"time":388361,"text":"to interact and study together,"},{"time":390715,"text":"and also to reduce the time\nour professors need"},{"time":395778,"text":"to labor over class assignments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401006,"text":"If the Internet has made us\na global village,"},{"time":406232,"text":"this model can develop\nits future leadership."},{"time":410378,"text":"Look how we do it."},{"time":412251,"text":"We only offer two programs:"},{"time":415079,"text":"business administration\nand computer science,"},{"time":417776,"text":"the two programs most in demand worldwide,"},{"time":421958,"text":"the two programs that are likeliest\nto help our students find a job."},{"time":427512,"text":"When our students are accepted,"},{"time":430274,"text":"they are placed in a small classroom\nof 20 to 30 students,"},{"time":436161,"text":"to ensure that those who need\npersonalized attention get it."},{"time":440827,"text":"Moreover, for every nine-week course,\nthey meet a new peer,"},{"time":446614,"text":"a whole new set of students\nfrom all over the world."},{"time":450129,"text":"Every week, when they go\ninto the classroom,"},{"time":453409,"text":"they find the lecture notes of the week,"},{"time":456166,"text":"the reading assignment,\nthe homework assignment,"},{"time":458454,"text":"and the discussion question,\nwhich is the core of our studies."},{"time":462405,"text":"Every week, every student must contribute\nto the class discussion,"},{"time":466887,"text":"and also must comment\non the contribution of others."},{"time":471109,"text":"This way, we open our students' minds,"},{"time":474631,"text":"we develop a positive shift in attitude\ntoward different cultures."},{"time":480089,"text":"By the end of each week,\nthe students take a quiz,"},{"time":483854,"text":"hand in their homework,"},{"time":485201,"text":"which are assessed by their peers\nunder the supervision of the instructors,"},{"time":490292,"text":"get a grade, move to the next week."},{"time":492566,"text":"By the end of the course,\nthey take the final exam,"},{"time":495236,"text":"get a grade, and follow\nto the next course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500703,"text":"We open the gates for higher education\nfor every qualified student."},{"time":506855,"text":"Every student with a high school diploma,"},{"time":509793,"text":"sufficient English and Internet connection"},{"time":512957,"text":"can study with us."},{"time":514573,"text":"We don't use audio, we don't use video."},{"time":517505,"text":"Broadband is not necessary."},{"time":519889,"text":"Any student from any part of the world\nwith any Internet connection"},{"time":524492,"text":"can study with us."},{"time":526798,"text":"We are tuition free."},{"time":529202,"text":"All we ask our students to cover\nis the cost of their exams,"},{"time":532843,"text":"100 dollars per exam."},{"time":535396,"text":"A full-time bachelor's degree\nstudent taking 40 courses"},{"time":540020,"text":"will pay 1,000 dollars a year,"},{"time":542867,"text":"4,000 dollars for the entire degree."},{"time":545521,"text":"And for those who cannot afford even this,"},{"time":549121,"text":"we offer them a variety of scholarships."},{"time":551895,"text":"It is our mission that nobody\nwill be left behind"},{"time":554973,"text":"for financial reasons."},{"time":557058,"text":"With 5,000 students in 2016,\nthis model is financially sustainable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565352,"text":"Five years ago, it was a vision."},{"time":569813,"text":"Today, it is a reality."},{"time":572862,"text":"Last month, we got the ultimate\nacademic endorsement to our model."},{"time":578325,"text":"University of the People\nis now fully accredited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582743,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584029,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585277,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":589386,"text":"With this accreditation,\nit's our time now to scale up."},{"time":594179,"text":"We have demonstrated that our model works."},{"time":598404,"text":"I invite universities\nand, even more important,"},{"time":601416,"text":"developing countries' governments,"},{"time":603109,"text":"to replicate this model"},{"time":605039,"text":"to ensure that the gates of higher\neducation will open widely."},{"time":610490,"text":"A new era is coming --"},{"time":612450,"text":"an era that will witness the disruption\nof the higher education model"},{"time":617767,"text":"as we know it today,"},{"time":619931,"text":"from being a privilege for the few"},{"time":623658,"text":"to becoming a basic right,\naffordable and accessible for all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":629779,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631122,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}